on regarding the paywall for in-depth transit analysis. (trade-off: deprioritize Pause the meditation library expansion — optimizing current conversion funnels yields higher immediate ROI.)\n[...]\n| Metric | Value |\n| --- | --- |\n| Overall Rating | 4.91/5 |\n| Total Reviews | 58.3K |\n| Sentiment | Thrilled (92/100) |\n| Confidence | High |\n| Pricing Model | Freemium |\n| Platforms | iOS & Android |\n| Key Features | 3 analyzed |\n| Trend | Mixed |\n| Outlook | Stable |\n[...]\n### Is CHANI worth paying for if I am a beginner?\n[...]\nCHANI offers extensive free content including daily horoscopes and birth chart overviews. Premium features like detailed transits and meditation libraries are best suited for users who want to build a daily astrological ritual, but beginners can get significant value from the free tier.\n\n---\n\nTitle: CHANI: Your Astrology Guide UI Breakdown | ScreensDesign Showcase\nURL: https://screensdesign.com/showcase/chani-your-astrology-guide\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\n$450.0K/mo25.0K downloads4.9 rating9 onboarding steps\n[...]\n**App info**\n* **App name:** CHANI: Your Astrology Guide\n* **Onboarding steps:** 9\n* **Paywall type:** Free Trial - Soft Paywall\n* **Monthly installs:** 25,000\n* **Monthly revenue:** $500,000\n* **App category:** lifestyle\n[...]\n* **Freemium Teasers:** Courses offer the first lesson for free (03:29), giving a substantial preview of premium content and creating a value-driven reason to subscribe.\n[...]\nCHANI uses a freemium model with a soft paywall. Users can access a significant amount of content for free, including daily horoscopes and the first lesson of some courses. The paywall appears when a user attempts to access locked content, such as a premium course lesson (03:34). The paywall screen (03:35) presents two free trial options, an annual plan with a discount and a monthly plan. This strategy allows users to experience the app's value and build trust before being asked to pay.","_me