{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_5rc47lijtaiw_4","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Title: You Were Born for This: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance: Nicholas, Chani: 9780063043770: Amazon.com: Books\nURL: https://amzn.to/3A3DDnU\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: Chani Nicholas       \n       \t\t\t (Author)\nHighlights:\nYou Were Born for This: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance: Nicholas, Chani: 9780063043770: Amazon.com: Books\n[...]\nChani Nicholas\n[...]\nPart of: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance (1 books)\n[...]\nFrom beloved astrologer Chani Nicholas comes an essential astrology guide for radical self-acceptance.\n[...]\nYour weekly horoscope is merely one crumb of astrology’s cake. In her first book You Were Born For This, Chani shows how your birth chart―a snapshot of the sky at the moment you took your first breath―reveals your unique talents, challenges, and opportunities. Fortified with this knowledge, you can live out the life you were born to. Marrying the historic traditions of astrology with a modern approach, You Were Born for This explains the key components of your natal chart in an easy to use, choose your own adventure style. With journal prompts, reflection questions, and affirmations personal to your astrological makeup, this book guides you along the path your chart has laid out for you.\n[...]\nChani makes the wisdom of your birth chart accessible with three foundational keys:\n[...]\n- The First Key: Your Sun (Your Life’s Purpose)\n- The Second Key: Your Moon (Your Physical and Emotional Needs)\n- The Third Key: Your Ascendant and Its Ruler (Your Motivation for Life and the Steersperson of Your Ship)\n[...]\nAstrology is not therapy, but it is therapeutic. In a world in which we are taught to look outside of ourselves for validation, You Were Born for This brings us inward to commit to ourselves and our life’s purpose.\n[...]\nAstrology for Radical Self-Acceptance\n[...]\n304 pages\n[...]\nFebruary 9, 2021\n[...]\n0063043777\n[...]\n978-0063043770\n\n---\n\nTitle: You Were Born For This\nURL: https://www.hachette.co.nz/book/?id=you-were-born-for-this-9781529394733\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nYou Were Born For This\n\nFacebook Instagram Twitter\n\nGo\n\nFacebook Instagram Twitter\n\nGo\n\n- About Us\n- Booksellers\n- Get Published\n- Browse\n- What’s On\n\nDownload 300dpi cover ↓\n\n# You Were Born For This\n\nTrade Paperback\n\n## Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance\n\n*THE NEW YORK TIMES BESTSELLER*\n\nChani Nicholas has amassed hundreds of thousands of loyal devotees for her radical approach to astrology for the real world - her first book is a modern day guide for using everyday astrology as a route to self-discovery, growth and finding purpose.\n\nGone are the whimsical musings of 'On Tuesday you will meet your prince charming' horoscopes - Nicholas is spearheading an empowering new approach. Challenging readers to take control, confront their emotions, supercharge their intentions and use the power of the stars to reach their true potential.\n\nIn an era when growing numbers of people are feeling a sense of meaninglessness and a desire to learn more about themselves, You Were Born for This teaches you how to harness the zodiac to become in tune with yourself and able to contextualise in an overwhelming world of confusing experiences and chaos.\n\nWith journal prompts, reflection questions and affirmations personal to your astrological make-up, this book guides you along the path your chart has laid out for you.\n\nBuy now!\n\nChecking availability in shops\n\n- Book Hero Checking availability\n- BookHub Checking availability\n- The Nile\n- Unity Books Checking availability\n- The Warehouse Checking availability\n- Paper Plus Checking availability\n- Whitcoulls Checking availability\n- Mighty Ape Checking availability\n- Manna Checking availability\n\n- Buy from your local bookstore. Find your closest one\n\n- Pub date: 29.12.20\n- Author: Chani Nicholas\n- ISBN: 9781529394733\n\n- Format: Paperback / softback\n- RRP: $29.99\n\n## Author\n\nDownload ↓\n\n### Chani Nicholas\n\nChani has written for and been featured in the New York Times, Los Angeles Times, Lenny Letter, Teen Vogue, Chicago Tribune, Huffington Post, Harper's Bazaar, The Cut, Bustle, Buzzfeed, Refinery29, Nylon and on Netflix. She has been a student of astrology since age 12 and a counselling astrologer for 20 years. She has a dedicated fan base of nearly 400,000 across her socials, with 130,000 subscribers to her weekly newsletter and monthly website traffic averaging between 600,000 and 1,000,000.\n\n## Other books by the author\n\n© 2026 Hachette Aotearoa | New Zealand. Website by CG Design.\n\n© 2026 Hachette Aotearoa | New Zealand. Website by CG Design.\n\nWHAT'S ON TEACHER’S RESOURCES ILLUSTRATION PRIZE BROWSE BOOKSELLERS MEDIA HUB ABOUT US & CONTACT GET PUBLISHED PRIVACY POLICY\n\nSearch\n\nClose\n\nAdded to basket\n\nCheckout Continue shopping\n\nGo\n\nE f I w\n\n---\n\nTitle: Summary of 'You Were Born for This' by Chani Nicholas\nURL: https://newbookrecommendation.com/summary-of-you-were-born-for-this-by-chani-nicholas/\nPublished: 2024-08-03T21:01:29.000Z\nAuthor: New Book Recommendation\nHighlights:\nWhat is You Were Born for This about? This book explores astrology as a pathway to radical self-acceptance. Chani Nicholas uses personalized birth charts to guide readers towards understanding their own unique strengths and challenges. The book encourages introspection through reflections, affirmations, and journal prompts, making astrology accessible for beginners.\n[...]\nTitle: You Were Born for ThisAuthor: Chani NicholasPublished: January 7, 2020Pages: 293 (Kindle Edition)Genre: Astrology, Nonfiction, Spirituality, Self Help\n[...]\nChani Nicholas presents “You Were Born for This,” a guide to radical self-acceptance through astrology. The book, a New York Times Bestseller, emphasizes understanding one’s birth chart. By examining your birth chart, you discover unique talents, challenges, and opportunities. This knowledge equips you to live authentically and purposefully. The book combines traditional astrology with a modern, engaging approach. It transforms astrology from vague horoscopes into a structured tool for personal growth.\n[...]\nthe world. This\n[...]\nsteering mechanism on your life\n[...]\ns journey. With these elements,\n[...]\ninsight into living\n[...]\nSome readers feel that the content lacks depth after initial impressions. Critics claim it caters mainly to astrology newbies. For those with prior knowledge, this book may present limited new information. Focus remains on the Sun, Moon, and Ascendant, with less emphasis on other aspects. Despite this, many find value in its clarity and accessible language. Nicholas’s vulnerability and honesty shine through her writing. She addresses themes like racial justice and personal responsibility, encouraging readers to reflect deeply.\n[...]\n- Radical Self-Acceptance: The book emphasizes accepting oneself fully through the lens of astrology.\n- Empowerment through Knowledge: Nicholas encourages readers to understand their birth charts to better navigate their lives.\n- Personal Reflection: The inclusion of journal prompts and affirmations prompts introspection and self-discovery.\n- Astrology as Therapy: While not a substitute for therapy, astrology is presented as a therapeutic tool for personal growth.\n- Intersectionality: Nicholas discusses issues of race, gender, and justice within the context of astrology.\n[...]\nChani Nicholas\n[...]\na well-known astrologer recognized for\n[...]\ninclusive and progressive approach.\n[...]\nChani Nicholas is an acclaimed astrologer known for her insightful writings that bridge astrology with social justice. Her work emphasizes healing and personal growth through astrological understanding.\n\n---\n\nTitle: You Were Born for This: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance by Chani Nicholas | Goodreads\nURL: https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/37959939-you-were-born-for-this\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nYou Were Born for This: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance by Chani Nicholas | Goodreads\n[...]\n# You Were Born for This: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance\n[...]\nThe beloved Los Angeles astrologer with more than one million fans shows a new generation how to use astrology as a tool for self-discovery, success, and self-care in this revolutionary guide.Modern astrology isn’t about passively accepting our fate, it’s about action, and beloved astrologer Chani Nicholas shows you how to bring this life-changing practice into your life and embrace self-empowerment, intentionality, and spirituality. Gone are the days of \"on Tuesday you will meet your prince charming\" horoscopes. Instead, Nicholas is spearheading a radical new approach to astrology. In her hip, inspirational weekly horoscopes, she doesn’t tell readers what will happen to them. Instead, she encourages her devotees to take control—to confront themselves, their desires, and their needs—to fulfill their potential using the power of the stars.Written in her lyrical, cool-girl, feminist writing style, You Were Born for This explains how knowing your star signs and what they mean for your individual character can be revelatory. Understanding the astrological chart can help you refine your intentions, identify your strengths, recognize areas for growth, become more connected to your core self, and steer you on your spiritual path.In an era when growing numbers of people feel a sense of meaninglessness and a desire to learn more about themselves, You Were Born for This teaches you how to harness the zodiac to help you become more in tune with yourself and your place in the universe.\n[...]\nFirst published January 7, 2020\n[...]\ncharacteristics of my sun sign\n[...]\nI’ve\n[...]\nstudy of the occult has\n[...]\n. Even though\n[...]\nbit about astrology\n[...]\nThree” placements in\n[...]\nchart AKA sun sign, moon sign and rising sign/ascendant\n[...]\nI’ve\n[...]\nexplained the twelve house system\n[...]\nI’ve\n[...]\nsextiles, trines, squares and oppositions) in a\n[...]\nthe house systems and aspects, I would\n[...]\nhave a confident grasp on these things, you\n[...]\nand ended up making five pages\n[...]\nI would definitely recommend\n[...]\nTaurus Moons\n[...]\nCancer Risings\n[...]\nPlease out yourselves in\n[...]\nI've\n[...]\nthose insights about\n\n---\n\nTitle: Our limited-edition 2024 bundles are officially here! | CHANI\nURL: https://chaninicholas.com/our-limited-edition-2024-bundles-are-officially-here/\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nEverything you need to know about 2024. Your 2024 Guidebook is a 100+ page digital resource with personalized readings, rituals, and affirmations to help you navigate the coming year. 2024 is filled to the brim with potent astrology, and it will impact you in different ways depending on your rising sign. Because of this, each guidebook is uniquely tailored to reflect the areas of life for that particular sign, meaning no two are alike. In your guidebook, we examine each astrological moment in detail and provide exercises to support you through every twist and turn. For added guidance, we recommend using it in conjunction with our Year Ahead readings (available on the CHANI app).\n[...]\nYour 2024 Guidebook includes:\n[...]\n- An overview of the astrology for 2024.\n- A detailed breakdown of how each major astrological moment will impact your life.\n- Rising-sign-specific rituals, exercises, and affirmations to help you work with the astrology as it unfolds.\n- Bulleted takeaways on how the main planetary ingresses and transits of the year will affect key areas of your life — with tips on how to make the most of them.\n[...]\n- A list of the year’s primary transits, ingresses, and retrogrades — including New and Full Moons, lunar and solar eclipses, Mercury retrogrades, and more.\n[...]\n- Astro 101 cheat sheets to familiarize yourself with the signs, houses, and planets.\n[...]\n- A glossary of key terms to aid you in your astrological studies.\n[...]\n- A format that’s compatible with assistive technology, such as screen readers\n[...]\nis “choice\n[...]\nthe magic happens when you trust yourself to pick a path. This next spin around the Sun offers deep personal healing as well\n[...]\nWhatever heart aches and\n[...]\n, dreaming expansively,\n[...]\n” to manifest your desires as\n[...]\n### You Were Born for This: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance\n[...]\nYour essential guide for radical self-acceptance. In this New York Times Best Seller, Chani Nicholas shows you how your birth chart reveals your unique life path, purpose, gifts, challenges, and opportunities. Marrying the historic traditions of astrology with a modern approach, You Were Born for This explains the key components of your birth chart — i.e., your Sun (your life’s purpose), your Moon (your physical and emotional needs), and your ascendant and its ruler (your motivation for living life and the steersperson of your ship) — in an easy-to-use, choose-your-own-adventure style. Through journal prompts, reflection questions, and affirmations personal to your astrological makeup, it guides you along the path your chart has laid out for you so that you can live the life you were born to."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"071762b9-140f-4c64-af75-f70aaa42db96","uuid":"f78a48f8-4078-4bc9-9912-7bc592f91789","timestamp":"2026-06-10T18:52:10.953Z","tool_use_result":[{"type":"text","text":"Title: You Were Born for This: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance: Nicholas, Chani: 9780063043770: Amazon.com: Books\nURL: https://amzn.to/3A3DDnU\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: Chani Nicholas       \n       \t\t\t (Author)\nHighlights:\nYou Were Born for This: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance: Nicholas, Chani: 9780063043770: Amazon.com: Books\n[...]\nChani Nicholas\n[...]\nPart of: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance (1 books)\n[...]\nFrom beloved astrologer Chani Nicholas comes an essential astrology guide for radical self-acceptance.\n[...]\nYour weekly horoscope is merely one crumb of astrology’s cake. In her first book You Were Born For This, Chani shows how your birth chart―a snapshot of the sky at the moment you took your first breath―reveals your unique talents, challenges, and opportunities. Fortified with this knowledge, you can live out the life you were born to. Marrying the historic traditions of astrology with a modern approach, You Were Born for This explains the key components of your natal chart in an easy to use, choose your own adventure style. With journal prompts, reflection questions, and affirmations personal to your astrological makeup, this book guides you along the path your chart has laid out for you.\n[...]\nChani makes the wisdom of your birth chart accessible with three foundational keys:\n[...]\n- The First Key: Your Sun (Your Life’s Purpose)\n- The Second Key: Your Moon (Your Physical and Emotional Needs)\n- The Third Key: Your Ascendant and Its Ruler (Your Motivation for Life and the Steersperson of Your Ship)\n[...]\nAstrology is not therapy, but it is therapeutic. In a world in which we are taught to look outside of ourselves for validation, You Were Born for This brings us inward to commit to ourselves and our life’s purpose.\n[...]\nAstrology for Radical Self-Acceptance\n[...]\n304 pages\n[...]\nFebruary 9, 2021\n[...]\n0063043777\n[...]\n978-0063043770\n\n---\n\nTitle: You Were Born For This\nURL: https://www.hachette.co.nz/book/?id=you-were-born-for-this-9781529394733\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nYou Were Born For This\n\nFacebook Instagram Twitter\n\nGo\n\nFacebook Instagram Twitter\n\nGo\n\n- About Us\n- Booksellers\n- Get Published\n- Browse\n- What’s On\n\nDownload 300dpi cover ↓\n\n# You Were Born For This\n\nTrade Paperback\n\n## Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance\n\n*THE NEW YORK TIMES BESTSELLER*\n\nChani Nicholas has amassed hundreds of thousands of loyal devotees for her radical approach to astrology for the real world - her first book is a modern day guide for using everyday astrology as a route to self-discovery, growth and finding purpose.\n\nGone are the whimsical musings of 'On Tuesday you will meet your prince charming' horoscopes - Nicholas is spearheading an empowering new approach. Challenging readers to take control, confront their emotions, supercharge their intentions and use the power of the stars to reach their true potential.\n\nIn an era when growing numbers of people are feeling a sense of meaninglessness and a desire to learn more about themselves, You Were Born for This teaches you how to harness the zodiac to become in tune with yourself and able to contextualise in an overwhelming world of confusing experiences and chaos.\n\nWith journal prompts, reflection questions and affirmations personal to your astrological make-up, this book guides you along the path your chart has laid out for you.\n\nBuy now!\n\nChecking availability in shops\n\n- Book Hero Checking availability\n- BookHub Checking availability\n- The Nile\n- Unity Books Checking availability\n- The Warehouse Checking availability\n- Paper Plus Checking availability\n- Whitcoulls Checking availability\n- Mighty Ape Checking availability\n- Manna Checking availability\n\n- Buy from your local bookstore. Find your closest one\n\n- Pub date: 29.12.20\n- Author: Chani Nicholas\n- ISBN: 9781529394733\n\n- Format: Paperback / softback\n- RRP: $29.99\n\n## Author\n\nDownload ↓\n\n### Chani Nicholas\n\nChani has written for and been featured in the New York Times, Los Angeles Times, Lenny Letter, Teen Vogue, Chicago Tribune, Huffington Post, Harper's Bazaar, The Cut, Bustle, Buzzfeed, Refinery29, Nylon and on Netflix. She has been a student of astrology since age 12 and a counselling astrologer for 20 years. She has a dedicated fan base of nearly 400,000 across her socials, with 130,000 subscribers to her weekly newsletter and monthly website traffic averaging between 600,000 and 1,000,000.\n\n## Other books by the author\n\n© 2026 Hachette Aotearoa | New Zealand. Website by CG Design.\n\n© 2026 Hachette Aotearoa | New Zealand. Website by CG Design.\n\nWHAT'S ON TEACHER’S RESOURCES ILLUSTRATION PRIZE BROWSE BOOKSELLERS MEDIA HUB ABOUT US & CONTACT GET PUBLISHED PRIVACY POLICY\n\nSearch\n\nClose\n\nAdded to basket\n\nCheckout Continue shopping\n\nGo\n\nE f I w\n\n---\n\nTitle: Summary of 'You Were Born for This' by Chani Nicholas\nURL: https://newbookrecommendation.com/summary-of-you-were-born-for-this-by-chani-nicholas/\nPublished: 2024-08-03T21:01:29.000Z\nAuthor: New Book Recommendation\nHighlights:\nWhat is You Were Born for This about? This book explores astrology as a pathway to radical self-acceptance. Chani Nicholas uses personalized birth charts to guide readers towards understanding their own unique strengths and challenges. The book encourages introspection through reflections, affirmations, and journal prompts, making astrology accessible for beginners.\n[...]\nTitle: You Were Born for ThisAuthor: Chani NicholasPublished: January 7, 2020Pages: 293 (Kindle Edition)Genre: Astrology, Nonfiction, Spirituality, Self Help\n[...]\nChani Nicholas presents “You Were Born for This,” a guide to radical self-acceptance through astrology. The book, a New York Times Bestseller, emphasizes understanding one’s birth chart. By examining your birth chart, you discover unique talents, challenges, and opportunities. This knowledge equips you to live authentically and purposefully. The book combines traditional astrology with a modern, engaging approach. It transforms astrology from vague horoscopes into a structured tool for personal growth.\n[...]\nthe world. This\n[...]\nsteering mechanism on your life\n[...]\ns journey. With these elements,\n[...]\ninsight into living\n[...]\nSome readers feel that the content lacks depth after initial impressions. Critics claim it caters mainly to astrology newbies. For those with prior knowledge, this book may present limited new information. Focus remains on the Sun, Moon, and Ascendant, with less emphasis on other aspects. Despite this, many find value in its clarity and accessible language. Nicholas’s vulnerability and honesty shine through her writing. She addresses themes like racial justice and personal responsibility, encouraging readers to reflect deeply.\n[...]\n- Radical Self-Acceptance: The book emphasizes accepting oneself fully through the lens of astrology.\n- Empowerment through Knowledge: Nicholas encourages readers to understand their birth charts to better navigate their lives.\n- Personal Reflection: The inclusion of journal prompts and affirmations prompts introspection and self-discovery.\n- Astrology as Therapy: While not a substitute for therapy, astrology is presented as a therapeutic tool for personal growth.\n- Intersectionality: Nicholas discusses issues of race, gender, and justice within the context of astrology.\n[...]\nChani Nicholas\n[...]\na well-known astrologer recognized for\n[...]\ninclusive and progressive approach.\n[...]\nChani Nicholas is an acclaimed astrologer known for her insightful writings that bridge astrology with social justice. Her work emphasizes healing and personal growth through astrological understanding.\n\n---\n\nTitle: You Were Born for This: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance by Chani Nicholas | Goodreads\nURL: https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/37959939-you-were-born-for-this\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nYou Were Born for This: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance by Chani Nicholas | Goodreads\n[...]\n# You Were Born for This: Astrology for Radical Self-Acceptance\n[...]\nThe beloved Los Angeles astrologer with more than one million fans shows a new generation how to use astrology as a tool for self-discovery, success, and self-care in this revolutionary guide.Mo